  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\"><img alt=\"House Templeton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/50px-House_Templeton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/75px-House_Templeton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/100px-House_Templeton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Luceon Templeton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\"><img alt=\"House Templeton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/50px-House_Templeton.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/75px-House_Templeton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Templeton.svg/100px-House_Templeton.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Ninestars\" title=\"Knight of Ninestars\">Knight of Ninestars</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\">House Templeton</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Luceon Templeton</b> was an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Ninestars\" title=\"Knight of Ninestars\">Knight of Ninestars</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Templeton\" title=\"House Templeton\">House Templeton</a> during the latter stage of the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luceon_Templeton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Luceon fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Seven_Stars\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle of Seven Stars\">Battle of Seven Stars</a> beneath the banner of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Artys_Arryn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Artys Arryn\">Artys Arryn</a>. He is one of the candidates for the man who slew King <a href=\"/index.php/Robar_II_Royce\" title=\"Robar II Royce\">Robar II Royce</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Luceon_Templeton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Ninestars\" title=\"Knight of Ninestars\">Knight of Ninestars</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Ninestars_(First_Blackfyre_Rebellion)\" title=\"Knight of Ninestars (First Blackfyre Rebellion)\">Templeton</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404052543\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: